message:
Hey Brian,

Great connecting with you over LinkedIn!

Funny enough, my grandmother was visiting San Francisco, from Arizona, a few weeks back and mentioned that she had a friend there, who had a daughter, who had a son, who had a friend, etc. etc. ;) who was going to reach out.

Happy to setup a time to catchup over Skype or Google hangouts and talk about some of the interesting stuff we're working on. Study Sauce (https://studysauce.com/) looks like a useful tool; I've always had an issue throughout college keeping track of deadlines, etc. and ended up buying a huge calendar for my wall to pre-input my syllabus deadlines at the beginning of the semester, etc.

Anyhow, great meeting and hope to talk to you soon.

Best,
Brady Gentile
